. P.S. Did you really read it all? Lol. If you consider yourself as a "hardcore fps shooter player and cod is for kids bla bla bla" - try arma, waste your time, enjoy true hardcore. P.P.S. I was really bored so i wrote all this. Don't blame me, please.
