Rick (Feral Circus);-;If you love to simulate and experience LARGE scale combat (of any type) then you should own this right NOW... The ability to create literally any scenario that your mind can imagine using the mission editor, which is like Photoshop but for creating vile horrific wars instead of pretty pictures :-) Don't try to compare ARMA to any other FPS! This isn't just a game, it is a lesson... It will teach you how to understand ballistics and engage targets at long range using scopes correctly. You will learn how to read a topographical map & compass properly. It will make you understand the importance of team work. BUT MOST IMPORTANTLY you will get to experience shooting the living fu@k out of all your friends :-) With TrackIR (head tracking) + a good sound mod this really is the ultimate MILSIM I've been waiting for a game like this ever since I used to play Blitz on my Commodore VIC-20 lol Just gets better and better EVERYONE NEEDS THIS...
