rubixpieguy;-;Gameplay Arma 3's gameplay is unique and realistic. Unlike Call of Duty and Battlefield (which don't get me wrong are great games in their own ways). The controls can be quite hard to get used to in the ARMA series if your new, this game does involve a steep learning curve. But once you've learnt the controls you'll be good at the game it takes time and thats why I think people hesistate to buy Arma 3 or any ARMA game in general cause theres such a steep learning curve to it. Arma 3 is a great military simulator and simulates it very well. Graphics Arma 3 has amazing graphics if you can run it on Ultra and with FSAA and ATOC.. Oh yeah and don't forget to put sharpen filter on 100 otherwise you're game can and will look really blurry. When running on Ultra, Arma 3 will give you some FPS drops every now and then especially when theres alot of AI and or players around. Maps and Details Arma 3 goes across two maps. Altis and Stratis. Though the buildings are empty the map isn't designed to put objects in there, only missions do. Though it does reduce lag when playing around in the editor. Other than that the maps are great and I love to play on both of them. Community Arma 3 has one of the best and most helpful communities I've have ever seen. Though the modding community is all over the place and not all mods are compatible. Very rarely do you get hackers on Arma 3. Because its not a really popular game amongst hackers. Unlike Call of Duty or Battlefield. Developers Arma 3 has a Dev Team that still develops the game regardless of the haters. They have developed this game for over 2 years now and its just amazing how much content they've added since then. Like weapon resting, shooting from the back of cars and helicopters, bipods and alot more. They are one of the best Dev Teams I've come across and hope they don't abandon Arma 3's development. Downloadable Content Bohemia Interactive have released three DLCs so far. Karts, Helicopters and Marksmen DLCs and alot of free platform updates. But some think its way to expensive for two helicopters. But they put alot of effort in the Helicopters DLC to make sure its working proply before we get our hands on it . A platform update also gets released with every DLC :D Overall Overall? I think the game is great and for 60.00 AUD I think it is the best money I've spent on games in my whole life. So I recommend you buy this game. Just go buy it NOW I TELL YOU NOW! FINAL RATING = 10/10 RubixPieGuy Approved
