emy knew if that light found them they were done for. Its funny something as simple as a light could be so fun and deadly...10/10 for Amra 3!!!!!!! Here's a quick video on how to get to the AO faster than your opponent gaining an advantage during the entire match. View it on Youtube in your regular browser for HD. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=whZPLF5wBmU Another in game dropping guys off https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fees1RcjsBY
