Reyja 187;-;ARMA 3? Should you get it? That Depends. What is it? A Future War Simulation game. Pros: Large Maps Large Weapon Selection Fully Upgradable Weapons Large Vehicle Selection Large Community Large Variety of Game-Modes. Cons: Goes from very slow-based action to sudden moments of speed... It can be disorientating. You will die many, many times. You will rage many, many times. Your game will bug out many times. You will randomly disconnect from servers, many times. You will have no-idea what you're doing, many times. You will accidentally crash your car and burn to death, many, many times. You will spend 90% of your time customising your character only to die and have to repeat it.
