ayable. I dont know why either. There is something seriously wrong either with the servers, or there is something wrong with the way stuff is optimised and implemented in this game. Please note arma 3 has been released for a very long time now, ok yes its not full release. BUT MY GOD PLEASE FIX THE MULTIPLAYER BOHEMIA it makes your company look rediculous. dayz SA is in alpha and it manages to run 1000% better multiplayer arenas. Now my last qualm is the price. 60 dollars for something that has an unplayble mulitplayer and an unfinished single player????? HOLY @$%! My advice is very sadly. do not buy this game until full release :( and even then make sure it works properly or you may be wasting your money
